<div id="review_2442949454" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2442949454" />
    <a title="Kevin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/54965592-kevin"><img alt="Kevin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1460761461p2/54965592.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2442949454?book_show_action=true">Jul 24, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kevin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kevin" href="/user/show/54965592-kevin">Kevin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780671211974" href="/book/show/5064111-lame-deer-seeker-of-visions">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2442949454" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3904619403447696059">I college theology I only read the chapters that were going to be on the test. Some of the religious element fades into the background when the work is taken as a whole. Still, it&apos;s funny, infuriating, and thought-provoking.</span>
  <span id="freeText3904619403447696059" style="display:none">I college theology I only read the chapters that were going to be on the test. Some of the religious element fades into the background when the work is taken as a whole. Still, it's funny, infuriating, and thought-provoking.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3904619403447696059" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


