        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1585316390" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2394789788381498290">This book is about the life and times of John (Fire) Lame Deer, a Lakota holy man. It is based on talks and visits that Richard Erdoes had with Lame Deer, so it is a recorded oral history consisting of memories, experiences, observations of white culture, etc. My only complaint is that it rambles in places.</span>

          </span>
